{"tid":1529682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界和理非召集！抵制MTR點可以唔預埋遊客？？？","createTime":"2019-09-01T19:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:30:37.000Z","uid":79382,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e796b764317f2ca02934cb0d0beec358dda1000","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:26:41.000Z","msg":"好多人話罷去狗鐵商場，<br />\n但問心，香港人講抵制同支那人反日差唔多，<br />\n同埋旺區商場好多都係靠遊客賺錢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時大家去旅行plan行程，<br />\n都會睇Google Maps啲評價，<br />\n外國人嚟香港都一樣！！！<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家盡情去Google Maps搵返啲狗鐵商場，<br />\n可以直接zoom近去撳商場個名，<br />\n或者search商場嘅英文名，<br />\n然後<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>畀1星</strong></span></span>，最重要係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>用英文簡介狗鐵喺831點樣殘害市民！</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢完全合法，<br />\n唔會俾狗捉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會傷到人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正零成本又可以玩嘢，點解唔做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947bd9a20bf9695b985496cb24a37aa27a9d836f","tid":1529682,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"有幾多會真係睇<br />\n<br />\n揾人喺出入口/交通工具附近派埋傳單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我至今都未見到有人喺罷買罷食嘅公司附近提人唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f581e5b369ed44450625bbf39e562987b46f69b","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:38:09.000Z","msg":"MTR有份嘅商場：<br />\n<br />\n德福廣場一、二期（九龍灣站）<br />\n杏花新城（杏花邨站）<br />\n青衣城一、二期（青衣站）<br />\n綠楊坊（荃灣站）<br />\n奧海城一、二期（奧運站）<br />\n圓方（九龍站）<br />\n連理街（坑口站）<br />\n駿景廣場（火炭站）<br />\n屯門海趣坊（屯門碼頭站）<br />\n新屯門中心（屯門輕鐵車廠站）<br />\n屯門恆福商場（屯門三聖站）<br />\nPopCorn、PopCorn2（將軍澳站）<br />\n東薈城（東涌站）<br />\nTHE LOHAS（康城站）<br />\n沙田 CityLink（沙田站）<br />\n柴灣 新翠商場（柴灣站）"},{"pid":"84059b53deae1eeb67ac3081e2397b2d466aca72","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"947bd9a20bf9695b985496cb24a37aa27a9d836f","tid":1529682,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"有幾多會真係睇<br />\n<br />\n揾人喺出入口/交通工具附近派埋傳單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我至今都未見到有人喺罷買罷食嘅公司附近提人唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:40:05.000Z","msg":"Comments未必會仔細睇，<br />\n但評分都重要！<br />\n跟住個list搵商場，<br />\n放工返屋企嗰程車都做完啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e7aa5866ae2388f7473eb475cf9ca82372e37e","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:42:40.000Z","msg":"902 903<br />\n全港大三罷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529dd05280bedcd28aedc6bb37b7b20e49cff68c","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學生哥起身罷課未啊"},{"pid":"d80dad42decba66107e283afc7c5355c1f55310d","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61fa6c76c47a6b66ad1aea3dfde1d7e06d7025b","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"全港三罷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bf7656eb9653b8b6ab5d1aebd5880f6cdcb0a9","tid":1529682,"uid":79382,"like